{
  "eval_set_id": "full_pipeline",
  "name": "Full pipeline scenarios (REQUIRES live Telegram + Imagen + Veo)",
  "description": "Covers the human-in-the-loop scenarios from the playbook: (a) high-significance approve → Editor approve, (d) Topic Gate skip → Memory Bank human-rejected, (e) Editor revise-with-feedback → revision_writer rewrites. These cases fire real Telegram and (for a/e) generate real images/video. Do NOT run in CI — only run interactively when you can drive Telegram approvals AND have Veo + Imagen quota in the project. To run: set TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, TELEGRAM_APPROVAL_CHAT_ID, GCS_ASSETS_BUCKET, then `agents-cli eval run --evalset tests/eval/evalsets/full_pipeline.evalset.json`.",
